Milestone 1 — Extract Frames From Camera Video
    src/preprocessing/frame_extraction.py
    - Extracted 50 frames from each folder (left, right, wide)
    20 seconds and 30 FPS ≈600 frames
    600 frames × 3 cameras = 1800 frames
    For a PoC, we only need to prove the pipeline works. So we use: first 50 frames

    Utility : We Need src/data_loader/clip_selector.py
    Right now your folders contain 100+ clips per sensor.
    But not all clips may exist in every sensor.We must find clips that exist in:
        camera_front_wide
        camera_cross_left
        camera_cross_right
        lidar_top_360
        This script will automatically find those.
        Dataset verified: camera + lidar synchronization ✓

Milestone 2: Implementation of camera object detection.
    required : pip install ultralytics opencv-python
    src/detection/camera_object_detection.py
    Output : 
    outputs/
        camera_detections/
            front_wide/
            cross_left/
            cross_right/

        detection_json/
            front_wide/
            cross_left/
            cross_right/
    
    This JSON will be used later to:
        project lidar points into camera
        find points inside bbox
        cluster points
        generate 3D bounding boxes


Milestone 3 — Timestamp Alignment
    purpose : match camera frames with lidar scans
    src/preprocessing/timestamp_alignment.py

Milestone 4 — LiDAR decoding
    The LiDAR file contains:
        draco_encoded_pointcloud
        We must decode it to obtain:(X, Y, Z) 3D points

Milestone 5 — LiDAR → Camera Projection
    src/projection/lidar_to_camera_projection.py
    Goal:
        3D lidar point
        ↓
        camera coordinate system
            ↓
        camera intrinsics
            ↓
        image pixel
    Example:
        LiDAR point (3.5m, -1.2m, 12.4m)
         ↓
        Pixel (742, 385)

Milestone 6 — Extract LiDAR Points Inside YOLO Bounding Boxes
    Use camera detections to identify which LiDAR points belong to an object.
    src/labeling/extract_lidar_points_from_bbox.py

Milestone- 7 —Generate 3D Bounding Boxes from LiDAR Points
    We Generate 3D Bounding Boxes from LiDAR Points
        YOLO detection
            ↓
        LiDAR points inside bbox
            ↓
        DBSCAN clustering
            ↓
        3D bounding box